main event: On 13 August 1965 at 12:35 AM UTC, two unidentified flying objects were observed in Albany, New York.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 30 seconds and involved ground-visual sighting of two objects,The witness reported the objects were silver and made no noise,The objects appeared to be flying low at about 15 feet off the ground,The witness had previously seen several unidentified objects over the years around Albany,The report mentions interest in UFOs and a request for follow-up information from the Air Force.
sighted object: two silvery objects flying in the sky
witness description: a female, age 62, who has been interested in UFO research and has seen several unidentified objects previously.
